Michelle BECKNER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4678 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 30, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's motion to dismiss petition for belated appeal is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is accepted. The petition for belated appeal is dismissed.
